<h1>Daily Plan: Tuesday, December 31, 2025 (Year-End Wrap-Up)</h1>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p><strong>Context:</strong> Final working day of 2025. Complete year-end audit and documentation; finalize all Dec 26-31 accomplishments; prepare sustainable workflow entry for 2026.</p>

<p><strong>Objectives:</strong> 2 Priority Tasks - Comprehensive Dec 26-31 year-end audit, sustainable workflow documentation for 2026 launch.</p>

<h2>Priority 1: Comprehensive Year-End Audit (Dec 26-31)</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Generate final audit report for entire Dec 26-31 sprint; document all code changes, features completed, plans delivered.</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Run Daily Audit Agent:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Aggregate Dec 26, 27, 28, 29, 30, 31 chat histories</li>
<li>Generate comprehensive audit_2025-12-31.md (final audit of the sprint)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Code Changes Summary:</strong>
<ul>
<li>List all files modified across 6 days</li>
<li>Document schema changes, API additions, UI/UX improvements</li>
<li>Count total lines added/removed/modified</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Plans Completed:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Mark Plan A.3 (Credentials Audit) as COMPLETE</li>
<li>Mark Plan E.1 Phase 3 as COMPLETE if widget functional</li>
<li>Update Plan F.1 status (architecture complete, implementation in progress)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Metrics & KPIs:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Days of work: 6 (Dec 26-27, 29-31; Dec 28 was internal planning)</li>
<li>Chats executed: ~40+ (estimated Dec 26-31)</li>
<li>Features delivered: 2-3 (A.3 credentials, E.1 phase 3 widget, F.1 architecture)</li>
<li>Bugs fixed: Document any critical fixes from daily audits</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 1.5-2 hours | <strong>Deliverable:</strong> Comprehensive audit_2025-12-31.md with full sprint metrics</p>

<h2>Priority 2: Sustainable Workflow Documentation & 2026 Launch Preparation</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Document lessons learned from Dec 26-31 workflow; establish sustainable patterns for 2026; prepare Week 1 (Jan 2-4) entry point.</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Document Workflow Patterns:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Update `/Comserv/root/Documentation/daily_planning_workflow.md`</li>
<li>Record: What worked well (three-agent architecture, daily audits, master plan tracking)</li>
<li>Record: What needs improvement (IDE token limits with large files, /chathandoff checkpoint strategy)</li>
<li>Document: Daily execution pattern established Dec 26-31</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Update Master Plan Link for Jan 2:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Master plan link currently points to Dec 29</li>
<li>Update comment: Next update scheduled Jan 2, 2026 (Jan 1 is holiday)</li>
<li>Prepare for Week 2 continuous planning starting Jan 2</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Archive Dec 31 Session:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Execute final `/sessionhandoff` of 2025</li>
<li>Archive current_session.md → [TIMESTAMP]_session_archive.md</li>
<li>Reset current_session.md for Jan 2 work</li>
<li>Preserve all Dec 26-31 chat history in archive</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Validate 2026 Readiness:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Confirm all daily plans exist for Jan 2-5 (Week 1 resumption)</li>
<li>Verify master plan version is current (0.12 or higher)</li>
<li>Check three-agent architecture ready for Jan 2 test execution</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 1-1.5 hours | <strong>Deliverable:</strong> Updated workflow documentation; ready for Jan 2 restart</p>

